#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""Generate Povvo Spec-Scan GitHub profile widgets.

The pack contains six static SVG widgets and six animated GIF variants.
Only the Current Focus widget uses the exact production mark. The compact
production-mark raster is embedded here so the renderer remains self-contained.
Every animated widget also has a static SVG equivalent for reduced-motion use.
"""

